quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  28,1,"Ṭaa, Sɩɩn, Miim."
  28,2,"Ad woto yaa Gafã Aaya-rãmba sẽn yɑɑ vẽenegã."
  28,3,"Tõnd karemdame n togsd foom ne sɩda, sẽn yi a Musa la a Fɩr-ʿaoon kibarã sɩd-kõtbã yĩngɑ."
  28,4,"Ad a Fɩr-ʿaoon zẽka a meng tẽng zugu, n welg a tẽngã rãmbã, n yõg kẽerã n maan yembse, n kʋʋd b kom-ribli wã la a basd b kom-pugli wã vɩɩse, ad a yɩɩ sãamda."
  28,5,"Tɩ Tõnd tʋll n na n maan neb nins b sẽn valems-b tẽng zugã neere, lɑ D maan tɩ b lebg sɩd taoor rãmba, la D maan tɩ yaa bãmb la faad rɩkdbã."
  28,6,"La D kõ-b pãng tẽng zugu, la D wĩnig a Fɩr-ʿaoon la a Ḥaamaan la b yiibã tãb-biisã b sẽn da yɩ n yaeesdẽ wã."
  28,7,"La Tõnd leemsɑ ɑ Musa ma wã t'ɑ yẽsem-a la f sã n yεεsd a zugu, bɩ f rɩk-a n ning kʋlgã pʋga, la f ra yεεs ye, la ra sãam f sũur ye, ad Tõnd na n lebs-ɑ-lɑ fo nengẽ la D mɑɑn-ɑ t'a yɩ Tẽn-tʋʋma."
  28,8,"T'a Fɩr-ʿaoon zakã rãmb rɩk-a t'ɑ na n wɑ yɩ b bε la b sũ-sãanga ne bãmbɑ, ad a Fɩr-ʿaoon la a Ḥaamaan la b yiibã tãb-biisã yɩɩ tudgdba."
  28,9,"T'a Fɩr-ʿaoon pagã yeele: ""ad a na n yɩɩ nin-maagr n kõ maam ne foom, ra kʋ-a ye, tɩ tõe t'a wa naf tõndo, maa d rɩk-a t'a yɩ d biiga"". La b ra ka mi b yellã baasg sẽn nɑ n yɩ wã ye."
  28,10,"T'a Musa ma wã pεlgã lebg vʋɩɩgo (rẽndɑ ɑ yellã bɑl n pak-a); kellẽ-lɑ bilf t'a vẽnegẽ yellã, sã n ka Tõnd sẽn keng a sũurã sẽn na yɩl t'a yɩ sɩd-kõta."
  28,11,"La a yeel a Musa tãoã: ""pʋg-a n gese"". T'a gεt-ɑ yɩɩgɑ, tɩ b ka ning b yɑmẽ tɩ yɑɑ a tão ye."
  28,12,"Lɑ Tõnd rɑ reng n gɩdg-ɑ lɑme n yi pagb a taab yẽsengo, t'ɑ tãoã yeel-bɑ: "" m wĩnig-y zak rãmb sẽn na n zã-ɑ n kõ-y la b leb n nɑ n mɑɑn pʋ-peelem ne-a?"""
  28,13,"Tɩ Tõnd nɑ n lebs-a a ma wã nengẽ, sẽn na yɩl t'a nifã mɑɑge la a ra sãam a sũuri, la a bãng tɩ Wẽnd pʋlengã yaa sɩda, la ɑd nebã wʋsg fãa ka mi ye."
  28,14,"La a sẽn wa n ta a keelem wɑkato, Tõnd kõ-a-la Bʋʋd minim la bãngre, la yaa woto bɑl la Tõnd rond nin-sõmsã."
  28,15,"La a Mʋsɑ kẽe tẽngã pʋgẽ, b yam yaal-yaal wakate, n mik roap a yiib sẽn zabd taaba; a yembrã yaa yẽnda buudã neda, la a to wã yaa yẽnda bεεbã nedɑ, tɩ ned ning sẽn ya-a a buudã nedã bao t'a sõng-ɑ tɩ b zab ne b bε wã, t'a Musa na n toaag-a t'a vik n lʋɩ n ki. La a [Musa] yeel-yã: ""ad woto yaa a Sʋɩtãan soosgo, ad a yaa bε, n yaa menesd tɩ yaa vẽenega""."
  28,16,"T'ɑ yeele: ""M Soab a Wẽnde! ad mam wẽga m menga, bɩ f yaaf-ma. Tɩ Wẽnd na n yaaf-a, Ad A yaa yaafg Naab n yaa yolsg Naaba."
  28,17,"La a yeel-yã: ""M Soab a Wẽnde! ad Fo sẽn maan maam neema wã, m kõn leb n sõng nin-wẽnsã ye""."
  28,18,"Tɑ be tẽngã pʋgẽ n lebg yaeesdɑ n gũusd sẽn nɑ n yɩlɑ, la ned ning sẽn kos-yẽ sõngr zaamẽ wã moond-ɑ t'a wa sõng-a, la a Musa yeel-ɑ:""ad fo yaa kedgd tɩ yɑɑ n vẽnege""."
  28,19,"La a sẽn wa n rat n wẽbg ned ning sẽn ya-a b yiibã bε wã, la a [Musa nedã yaees n yeele: ""Musa, fo rat n kʋʋ maam wala fo sẽn kʋ yõor zaamẽ wã? Fo pa tʋll baa fʋɩ rẽnda fo na yɩ bi-bεεg bɑl tẽng zugu, fo pa rat n yɩ pɑɑsd ye""."
  28,20,"Tɩ rao yi tẽngã yaang n yãgdẽ n wɑ n yeele: ""Musa, ad kug-zĩidbã rɩkdɑ noor n rɑt n wa kʋ foom, bɩ f yi tẽngã, ad mam mɑɑnd-f-lɑ pʋ-peelem""."
  28,21,"T'ɑ yi tẽngã n yεεsdẽ n lɑmsdẽ n pɑ mi sẽn nɑ n yɩ ye, ɑ yeelɑme: ""M Soaba! tɩlg maam n yi wẽgdbã''."
  28,22,"La a sẽn wɑ n toglg Madyan sẽnẽ wã, a yeelame: ""tõe tɩ m Soabã peeg mɑɑm n tʋg so-tɩrga""."
  28,23,"La a sẽn wɑ n ta Madyan koomẽ (kʋlgẽ) wã, a mika zãma tɩ yũnugd b rũmsi, la a mik pagb a yiib sẽn lak n tɩ be kεεng n gɩdgd b rũmsã. t'ɑ yeele: ""yãmb yellã yɑɑ wãn-wãn tɩ y pɑ yũnugdẽ?"" tɩ b yiibã yeele: ""ad tõnd pa yũnugd d rũmsã hɑl tɩ rũm-kɩɩmbã wɑ looge, la tõnd saambã me yaa nin-kẽem-kʋdre""."
  28,24,"T'a yũnug n kõ b yiibã rũbsã n kõ-bɑ, rẽ poorẽ t'a kẽng maasmẽ wã, n yeele: ""m Soaba! Ad Fo sẽn sɩk bũmb ning n kõ mɑɑm sẽn yɑɑ sõmɑ fãɑ m tʋllɑme""."
  28,25,"Tɩ b a yiibã yembr wa a nengẽ n kẽnd ne yãn-zoεεga, n ta n yeele: "" ad m saambã boonda foom n na rol foo fo sẽn yũnug tõnd rũmsã keoore, la a Musa sẽn wa n ta b sɑɑmbã nengẽ wã, n togs-a ɑ kɩbayã, ɑ yeel-ɑ lame: ""ra yaees ye, ɑd fo põsɑ neb (ɑ Fɩrɑoon-rãmb) sẽn yɑɑ wẽgdbã""."
  28,26,"La b yiibã yembr yeel-yã: ""M saamba, rɩk-a t'ɑ gũud tõnd rũmsã, ad ned sõmblem sẽn yɩɩd fo sẽn nɑ n dɩk tʋʋmɑ, yɑɑ pãng soɑbã sẽn yaa bas-m-yam soabã""."
  28,27,"T'a yeele: ""mam rat n rɩka m kom-pugli a yiibã yembr n loe fur n kõ foom, la furã ligd yaa tɩ fo tʋm mam nengẽ yʋʋm a nii, la fo sã n pids yʋʋm piiga rẽ yɑɑ fo mɑɑn-neere, mam pa rat n nɑ n weoog foom ye, Wẽnd sã n sake, fo na n mika maam tɩ m yaa nin-sõngo""."
  28,28,"La a (Musa) yeel yã: ""woto yaa maam ne foom sʋka, wakat bãmbã b yiibã yembr mam sẽn wa n tõog n ta, beem ka be ne maam ye, la yaa Wẽnd la tõnd sẽn gomdã Bobenda""."
  28,29,"La a Musa sẽn wa n pids yʋʋmã, n loog ne a zakã rãmbã n nɑ n leb Mĩsrɑ, a yãɑ bugum tãngã kɩrengɑ, t'a yeel a zɑkã rãmbɑ: ""mɑm yãnda bugum, rɑɑr bɩ m pɑɑm kɩbɑr beenẽ n wa, maa m pɑɑm bug-vɩleng tɩ sãnd-sãnde y nɑ paam n woode''."
  28,30,"Lɑ ɑ sẽn wa n ta-a wã la B bool-ɑ ko-soogã rɩtg wεεngẽ, zĩig ning sẽn yaa barkã, tɩɩgẽ wã: n yeele ''Yaa fo a Musa! ad yaa Maam la Wẽnde, sẽn yɑ-ɑ bõn-naandã Soabã''"
  28,31,"La ""lobg f rasaarã"". La a sẽn wa n yã-a t'a rãmbdẽ tɩ yɑɑ wala waafã, a lebg n zoeeme, n pɑ lebgdẽ ye. T'A yeel-ɑ: ''Yaa fo a Musa! lebg la f ra yεεs ye, ad fo be bas-m-yam pʋgẽ''."
  28,32,"Rɩk f nugã n sui f loorẽ wã, t'a na n yiime n yɑɑ pεεlga, tɩ pa sẽer (bãag) ye. La f rɩk f nugã n pĩ f yãoogã tɩ yaeesgã sɑ. Rẽndɑ yaa tɑgmɑs a yiibu sẽn windi, tɩ yi fo Soɑbã nengẽ n tʋm tɩ f kẽng ne a Fɩr-ʿaoon la a kug-zĩidbã nengẽ, ad b ra yɩɩme n yaa dĩin-yitbɑ."
  28,33,"La a yeel yã: "" M Soaba Wẽnde! ad mam kʋʋ yõor b pʋgẽ wã, rẽnd mam yaeesda b na n wa kʋ maam n dole''."
  28,34,"La mam ma-biig a Haarʋʋnɑ, yẽndɑ yɩɩda maam ne zɩlem-pεka, bɩ F tʋms-a n naag maam t'a sõngd maam la a sɩdgd maam, ad m yaeesda b na n wa yags maam""."
  28,35,"T'A yeele: "" D na n kenga f pãngã ne f ma-biigã, la D maan wilb tɑgmas n kõ yãmb tɩ b ka tõe n mɑɑn yãmb wẽng ye. Sẽn tũ ne Tõnd tagmas-rãmbã, yãmb y yiibã la neb nins sẽn pʋg yãmbã n na n wili''."
  28,36,"La a Musa sẽn wa n wa b nengẽ ne Tõnd tɑgmas-rãmbã tɩ yɑɑ vẽenesã, la b yeel-yã: yãoã ka baa fʋɩ rẽnda tɩɩm sẽn wãag n dogle, tõnd pa wʋm yãoã kɩbar tõnd saam-rãmb nins sẽn deng taoorã nengẽ me ye."
  28,37,"La a Musa yeel yã: ""mam Soabã n yɩɩd minim ne ned ning sẽn wa ne kãndgr n yi A nengẽ, la A mi Yaoolem dɑɑrã baas neerã yaa ãnd nɑ n tɑll-ɑ; ad wẽg-m-mens-rãmbã ka tɩlgd ye""."
  28,38,"La a Fɩr-ʿaoon yeel yã: ""yaa yãmb mam kug-zĩidba! mam ka wĩnig yãmb soab zẽng n zʋʋg maam ye. Yaa foo a Ḥaamaana, yõgen tãndo n me gãsg n kõ maam tɩ m rʋ n tɩ tãag a Musa Soabã, mam pʋs n tẽedame t'a yagda zĩri""."
  28,39,"La a waooga a meng tẽng zugu, yẽnda la a tãb-biisã tɩ pa tũ ne sɩd ye. La b tẽ tɩ b pa na n lebg n wa Tõnd nengẽ ye."
  28,40,"Tɩ Tõng yõk-a la a sodaasã n lob-b mogrã pʋga. Bɩ f ges wẽgdbã baasg yɩɩ wãna?"
  28,41,"La Tõnd maan-b lame tɩ b yaa taoor rãmb n boond n tʋgd bugmẽ, la Yikr raarã b pa na n paam sõngr ye."
  28,42,"La Tõnd leb n pʋgl-b lame ne kãab-beed dũni kaanẽ, la Yikr raarã b na n zãag-b-la ne yolsgo."
  28,43,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd kõo a Musa Gafã, D sẽn halk rãeenem rãmbã zãma loogr poorẽ, tɩ yaa pʋ-tẽer ne nebã la kãndgr la yolsgo, tɩ raar ninga b na tẽegdẽ."
  28,44,"Lɑ ɑd fo pa zĩnd (Sɩnae) tãngã kɩreng sẽn teesd wĩntoog sẽn lʋɩtẽ, wakat ning Tõnd sẽn wa n tʋms tɩ kẽng a Musa nengẽ, fo ka yɩ kaset soɑb me wakat-kãng ye."
  28,45,"La ad Tõnd naana zãma rãmba, tɩ b zĩndgã wogle, lɑ fo ka yɩ zĩid Madyan tẽngã pʋgẽ n karemd Tõnd Aaya-rãmbã b zug ye, la ad Tõnd tʋm foo, lɑ D tʋms ɑ Musɑ kibɑrã (tɩ wa fo nengẽ) ."
  28,46,"La fo ka zĩnd tãngã kɩrenga, Tõnd sẽn wa n boolã wakat ye, la ad yaa yolsg sẽn yi fo Soabã nengẽ, sẽn na yɩl tɩ fo bugs neba, bugsd sẽn pa wa b nengẽ sẽn reng foom, tɩ raar ning b na tẽege."
  28,47,"Lɑ Masɩɩb sã n rag n paam-b lame, b sẽn tʋm zunuub tɩ reng taoor yĩnga, b rag n na n yeelame: ""yaa d Soaba! yaa bõe yĩng la Fo sẽn ka tʋms tẽn-tʋʋm tɩ wa tõnd nengẽ wã? Tɩ d paam n tũ Fo Aaya-rãmbã, la d paam n yɩ sɩd-kõtba?""."
  28,48,"La wakat ning sɩdã sẽn wa bãmbã, n yi Tõnd nengẽ wã, b yeelame: ""yaa bõe yĩng la b ka kõ-a tagmas sẽn wõnd a Musa rẽnda? ""la b yeele: "" tõnd pʋs n pa kõ sɩd ne baa a yembr ye!""."
  28,49,"Yeele: "" bɩ y wa ne gaf sẽn yi Wẽnd nengẽ t'a kãndgr yɩɩd bãmbã b yiibã, tɩ m na n pʋg-a lame, tɩ y sã n yɩ n yaa sɩd-rãmba''."
  28,50,"La ad b sã n ka tõog n wa ne gafã, bɩ f bãng tɩ b tũuda b yõe yamleoogo, la yaa ãnd n yɩɩd meneng n yɩɩd ned ning sẽn tũud a yõor yamleoogo, zẽng sẽn pa kãndgr sẽn yi Wẽnd nengẽ, ad Wẽnd pa kãnggd wẽgdb ye."
  28,51,"Ad Tõnd taas-b-la koeesã, tɩ raar ninga b na tẽege."
  28,52,"Neb nins Tõnd sẽn kõ Gafã, tɑoor tɩ Alkʋrãanã pɑ wɑ wã, b kõt-a-la sɩda."
  28,53,"La b sã n na n wa karem Alkʋrãanã b nengẽ, b yetdame: ""tõnd kõo sɩd ne-a, ad a yaa sɩd sẽn yi tõnd Soabã nengẽ, tõnd ra yɩɩme n yaa sak-n-tũ-rãmba taoor tɩ Alkʋrãɑnɑ pɑ wɑ ye."
  28,54,"B kõta bãmbã rãmbã b keoorã naoor a yiibu, b sẽn maan sugrã yĩnga la b sẽn rɩkd b yel-sõmdã n tusd yel-wẽnsã yĩnga, la b sẽn ra yɩ n yãkd Tõnd sẽn da kõ-b pʋɩɩr n maand doosã yĩnga."
  28,55,"Lɑ b sã n wa wʋm gom-yaals la b sẽn gũt b zãn-kuids la b yeele: ""tõnd tʋʋm n be ne tõndo, yãmb me tʋʋm n be ne yãmba, tɩlgr be ne yãmba, tõnd ka baood zɩtbã zĩigẽ ye''."
  28,56,"Ad fo ka kãndg fo sẽn nong-a soab ye, yaa Wẽnd n kãndgd A sẽn tʋll-ɑ, Yẽnda n leb n yɩɩd minim ne neb nins sẽn kãndã."
  28,57,"La b yeel yã: ""la tɩ tõnd sã n naag foom n tũ kãndgrã, b na n võoga tõnd n yiis d tẽngẽ wã"", - rẽ yĩnga Tõnd pa zĩndg yãmb Lohorem tẽngẽ, sẽn ya bas-m-yam tẽngã, tɩ tɩ-biis buud fãa kãagd n wat beenẽ, tɩ yaa pʋɩɩr sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ? La ad sẽn waoog fãa ka mi ye."
  28,58,"La sõor waoog Tõnd sẽn halk tẽms sẽn da maand kɩfndo ne Wẽnd neemã wã n pugd ne b vɩɩm sẽn da yaa noogo, ɑd bãmb zagsã yɑɑ sẽn lebg rɑboodo ned ka leb zĩnd be bãmb loogr poorẽ, sã n ka bilf bala sẽn so-loogdbã, la yaa Tõnd n dɩkd sɑɑs lɑ tẽng gill faado."
  28,59,"La fo Soabã ka yɩ n na n halk tẽngã, rẽndame t'A tʋms b nengẽ Tẽn-tʋʋma, t'a tɩ karem Tõnd Aaya-rãmbã b zugu, la ad Tõnd pa yɩ n na n halk tẽng rẽndame t'a nebã yaa wẽgdba."
  28,60,"Bũmb nins b sẽn kõ yãmbã fãa yaa dũni wʋm-noog la a faas teedo, la bũmb ning sẽn be Wẽnd nengẽ wã, yẽnd n yɩɩd sõmblem la paabo, rẽ yĩnga b pa tagsd n getẽ laa?"
  28,61,"Rẽ yĩnga ned ning Tõnd sẽn maan pʋlen-sõngo, t'a na n seg-a, yẽnda soab wõnda wala ned ning Tõnd sẽn maan dũni wʋm-noog n kõ-a, tɩ Yikr raarã a na n naaga neb nins b sẽn na n bʋ (Tõnd taoorã)?"
  28,62,"Lɑ raar ning Wẽnd sẽn na n wa bool-b n yeele: ""bõn-naands nins yãmb sẽn da yags zĩri tɩ yaa Mam lagem-n-taasã bεε?"""
  28,63,"Tɩ halkrã sẽn yaa tɩlae ne neb nins zugã yeele: ""yaa d Soaba! ad yaa bãmbã la sẽn menes tõndã. Tõnd menes-b lame wala b sẽn menes tõndã, tõnd foosa d nus n yi-ba, d lebg n waa Fo nengẽ: ad b rag n pa tũud tõnd ye''."
  28,64,"La b na n yeel-ba, bool-y y lagem-n-taasã! Tɩ b na n bool-ba, tɩ b pa sakdẽ ye. La b sã n wa yãnd naongã, b na n tʋllame n da yɩ kãndgdb Dũni kaanẽ."
  28,65,"La raar ning Wẽnd sẽn na n wa bool-ba n yeele: ""yãmb leoka tẽn-tʋʋmbã tɩ bõe?"""
  28,66,"Tɩ kibayã lebg lik ra-kãngã, tɩ b pa na n leb n sogs taab baa fʋɩ (sũ-sãɑg keelem)."
  28,67,"La sã n yaa ned ning sẽn tuub-a la a kõ sɩd la a maan tʋʋm sõmde, a tõe n wɑ naaga põsdbã."
  28,68,"La yaa fo Soabã n naand A sẽn tʋlle la A yãkdẽ, ad bãmbã ka tar yãkr ye, yɩlgemd be ne Wẽnd n yi b sẽn lagemd-A bũmb ninsã wã."
  28,69,"La fo Soabã mii bũmb ning b sũyã sẽn solgdã la bũmb ning b sẽn vẽnegdã."
  28,70,"Yaa Yẽnda la Wẽnde, soab ka be rẽnda Yẽnda. Yẽ n so pẽgr rãeenem (dũni zugu) la yaoolem. Bʋʋdã kaoob yaa Yẽnd n so, la yaa Yẽnda nengẽ la y na n lebg n kẽnge."
  28,71,"Yeele: ""yãmb yãame, rẽ yĩnga Wẽnd sã n maan yʋngã t'a kell n pa woto n tɩ tãag yikrã raare, sob-bʋg n tõe n kõ yãmb vẽenem zẽng tɩ pa Wẽnde? Rẽ yĩnga yãmb ka wʋmd la?"""
  28,72,"Yeele: ""yãmb yãame, rẽ yĩnga Wẽnd sã n maan wĩndgã t'a kell n pa woto n tɩ tãag yikrã raare, sob-bʋg n tõe n kõ yãmb yʋng tɩ yãmb vʋʋs a pɩgẽ zẽng tɩ pa Wẽnde?. Rẽ yĩnga yãmb ka ne la?"""
  28,73,"La sẽn be a yolsgã pʋgẽ la A sẽn maan yʋngã la wĩndgã n kõ yãmb sẽn na yɩl tɩ y vʋʋs a pʋgẽ la y bao Wẽnd neema wã, tɩ raar ninga y na pʋʋs barka."
  28,74,"Lɑ raar ning Wẽnd sẽn na n wa bool-b n yeele: ""bõn-naands nins yãmb sẽn da yagd zĩri tɩ yaa Mam lagem-n-taasã bεε?"""
  28,75,"La D yiis zãma pʋgẽ fãa b kaset soaba, rẽ poorẽ tɩ D yeele: ""wa-y ne y daliili"". Tɩ b bãng tɩ yaa Wẽnd n so sɩdã, tɩ bũmb ning b sẽn yagd zĩri n dogendẽ wã menem n bas-ba."
  28,76,"Ad a Ƙaarʋʋn rɑ yɑɑ a Musa nebẽ yembre, la a maan n zʋʋga b zugu, la Tõnd kõ-a-la arzεg-bεda, a kʋɩlen-biisã yaa zãma wʋsg sẽn tar pãng n tõe tʋke, t'a nebã yeel-a: ""ra maan waoog-m-meng ye, ad Wẽnd ka nong waoog-m-mens-rãmb ye,"
  28,77,"La rɩk arzεk ning Wẽnd sẽn kõ foomã n bao Yaoolem zĩigã, la ra yĩm f pʋɩɩrã dũni kaanẽ ye, la f tʋm tʋʋm sõama wala Wẽnd sẽn maneg n tʋg foomã, la ra wa bao sãang tẽngã zug ye, ad Wẽnd ka noang sãamdb ye""."
  28,78,"La a (Kaarʋʋn) yeel yã: ""ad mam sẽn paam arzεkã yaa sẽn tũ ne bãngr sẽn yi mam nengẽ"". Rẽ yĩnga yẽ ka bãng tɩ Wẽnd halka zãma sẽn reng yẽnda taoore, tɩ b pãng la b ligd ra yɩɩd yẽnda? La ad b ka bɑood n na n sok nin-wẽnsã b beegrã sẽn yɩlye ye."
  28,79,"La a (Kaarʋʋn) yi a nebẽ wã n be a faas teedã pʋgẽ, la neb nins sẽn rat dũni vɩɩmã yeel yã: ad tõnd ra tʋllame n paam wala a Kaarʋʋn arzεkã, ad a yaa zu-noog bedr soaba""."
  28,80,"La neb nins b sẽn kõ bãngrã rãmb yeel yã: ""wɩɩbd be ne yãmba, ad Wẽnd yel-sõmdã n yɩɩda ne ned ning sẽn kõ sɩda la a maan tʋʋm sõma"". La ka paamd woto rẽnda neb sẽn maan sugri."
  28,81,"Tɩ Tõnd kɩt tɩ tẽngã rɩ-a, yẽnda la a zakã, lɑ a ka paam tãp tɩ nɑ n sõng-a n põsg Wẽnd nɑongã ye, a leb n ka tõog n sõng a meng ye."
  28,82,"Tɩ neb nins sẽn dag n bʋ nonglem zaamẽ n rat n yɩ wala a Kaarʋʋn bilgrã yik yibeoog n yeele: ""Hã! Sã n yaa sɩda, ad Wẽnd yalgda arzεk n kõ A sẽn rat ned ninga, sẽn yi A yembsẽ wã, la A weoog kẽer rɩtla. Wẽnd sã n rag n ka maan A neema wã tõnd zugu, tẽngã rag n na n rɩɩ tõndo, ad kɩfr-rãmbã pa tɩlgd ye""."
  28,83,"Woto yaa yaoolem Roogã, D maand-a lame n kõ neb nins sẽn ka rat zẽk-m-meng la sãang tẽngã zugu. La ad yaoolem tɩlgrã bee ne Wẽn-zoεtbã."
  28,84,"Ned ning sẽn wa ne tʋʋm-sõngo, a tara keoor neerem sẽn yɩɩd rẽnda, la ned ning sẽn tʋm-a tʋʋm wẽnga, b pa na n rol neb nins sẽn maan tʋʋm wẽnsã rẽndame tɩ yaa b sẽn tʋmã bala."
  28,85,"Ad Naab ning sẽn sik-a Alkʋrãanã n maan-a t'a yaa tɩlae n rog fo zugã, A na n lebsa foom tɩ f kẽng Maka (n tɩ pak-a). Yeele: ""mam Soabã n yɩɩd minim ne ned ning sẽn wa-a ne kãndgre, la yaa Yẽnda n leb n yɩɩd minim ne ned ning sẽn be meneng sẽn yaa vẽeneg pʋga""."
  28,86,"Lɑ fo rag n ka tẽed tɩ b na n maana Gafã (Alkʋrãanã) wahɩ n kõ foom ye, ad woto yaa yolsg sẽn yi fo Soabã nengẽ, bɩ f ra yɩ sõngd ne kɩfr-rãmbã ye."
  28,87,"La bũmb ra wa gɩdg foom n yi Wẽnd Aaya-rãmbã, b sẽn sik-b n kõ foom poorẽ. La bool n tʋg fo Soabã sorẽ, la ra yɩ n naag lagem-n-taarã rãmb ye."
  28,88,"La ra wa bool n lagem Wẽnde soab zẽng ye. Soab ka be rẽnda Yẽnda, bũmb fãa na n halkame, rẽnda Yẽnda bala, Bʋʋdã yaa Yẽnd n so, lebgrã zĩig me yaa Yẽnda nengẽ."
